      228.13,
      515.46,
      282.84
    ],
    "text": "In connection with these investigations, on 01.04.2026, three suspects were apprehended within the Meegahawatte and Kandana Police Divisions for possessing vehicles without valid registration certificates. The vehicles included 03 cars, 02 jeeps, 01 lorry, and 01 motorcycle.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
