  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      99.37,
      366.43,
      112.65
    ],
    "text": "Fatal Road Accident \u2013 Saliyawewa Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      127.09,
      518.91,
      167.97
    ],
    "text": "On the evening of 01.04.2026, a lorry travelling towards Anuradhapura collided with a bicycle proceeding in the same direction at the 16th junction along the Puttalam\u2013Trincomalee Road within the Saliyawewa Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      182.53,
      525.94,
      223.41
    ],
    "text": "The cyclist, who sustained critical injuries in the accident, was initially admitted to the Aluthgama Hospital and subsequently transferred to the Puttalam Hospital for further treatment, where he later succumbed to his injuries.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      238.0,
      375.79,
      251.28
    ],
    "text": "The deceased is a 78-year-old resident of Rajanganaya.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      265.72,
      492.62,
      292.8
    ],
    "text": "The lorry driver involved in the accident has also been admitted to the Puttalam Hospital and is currently receiving medical treatment.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      307.36,
      412.99,
      320.64
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are underway by the Saliyawewa Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      334.73,
      526.89,
      370.44
    ],
    "text": "04. \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dd0\u0daf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dd0\u0daf \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dba \u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0db4\u0db1\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dd9 \u0db8\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0db4\u0dda \u0db4 \u0dbb\u0dc5\u0dd3",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota-Bold",
